Get ready to hit the track with Kart Race 3D, now available as a Chrome Extension! Experience the thrill of high-speed racing in vibrant 3D environments. Choose your kart, customize it, and race against opponents in exciting circuits filled with twists, turns, and challenges.

Compete for the best times, collect power-ups, and unlock new karts as you strive for victory. With smooth controls and engaging gameplay, Kart Race 3D brings the excitement of racing right to your browser. Start your engines and race to the finish line!
